<% provide(:title, "Home Blog")%>
<div class="main_title">
  <img src="/assets/lion-removebg-preview.png" alt="">
  <h1>Sample App | Home Blog</h1>
  <p>
    This is the home page for the 
    <a href="https://www.railstutorial.org/">Ruby on rails Tutorials</a>
